American Rivers has option on Opon stake . American Rivers Oil Co said Tuesday that it had signed an option to purchase an $ 8 . 5 million stake in Opon Development Co from Creston Exploration . The purchase option followed a May 9 announcement by AROC that Opon had decided not to pursue a previously proposed merger deal struck between the two companies . Opon ' s only asset is a 4 . 55 working interst in a gas field in Colombia , operated by Amoco Corp , American Rivers said . 
